    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Snap Quest》是一款温馨的摄影收集冒险与探索游戏。回到星岛，帮助你的祖母重新收集她丢失的研究资料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开岛上的各种谜题，拍摄生物和友善居民的照片。记录你的发现，将照片保存在你专属的研究日志中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成研究资助任务赚取资金，重建小岛。与小岛上的社区建立友谊，让这里重新繁荣起来！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327110/extras/bbf6a1a9d7bbdd6662c90458a1a077f0.poster.avif?t=1764266603\" width=600 height=395 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327110/extras/bbf6a1a9d7bbdd6662c90458a1a077f0.webm?t=1764266603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
